of heart function.

20:49.708 --> 20:51.293
I definitely did not.

20:51.376 --> 20:54.421
- Is this your signature at the bottom?
- When did I sign that?

20:54.505 --> 20:56.945
Right after you passed
the post-operative responsiveness test,

20:57.007 --> 20:58.884
legally mandated
by the state of New York.

20:58.967 --> 21:01.136
