what I was doing!

21:01.220 --> 21:02.846
You knew enough to sign your name.

21:02.888 --> 21:05.807
I dotted the "i" with a little love heart!

21:05.891 --> 21:08.310
You were happy to be alive, right?

21:09.353 --> 21:12.940
Now, about these hallucinations.
What are you seeing?

21:13.023 --> 21:14.233
People.

21:31.917 --> 21:33.460
Hey, got a sec?

21:37.172 --> 21:40.092
Never get used to that.
You're the guy, huh?

21:40.175 --> 21:43.303
No. I'm not the guy.
It's another guy. Go away.

21:43.387 --> 21:45.389
Real quick, got to hit you up for a favor.

21:45.430 --> 21:48.225
No, no, no, no.
No, he's still there. Unbelievable.

21:48.267 --> 21:51.186
- Thank you!
- Good, excellent. Thank you!

21:51.270 --> 21:52.855
Hey. Wait a minute. Wait, what?

21:52.938 --> 21:55.274
- Drive!
- No, no, no.

21:55.315 --> 21:57.150
- Where to, buddy?
- Don't do that!

21:57.234 --> 21:59.528
You're a busy little guy.
Let me get right to the point.

21:59.611 --> 22:01.488
That woman whose cab
you just snaked, that's my wife.

22:01.572 --> 22:03.365
- That's perfect.
- My widow.

22:03.448 --> 22:07.286
She's got a very serious problem.
I need your help to fix it.

22:07.327 --> 22:09.788
- Where do you want to go, pal?
- Tell him 54th and Madison.

22:09.830 --> 22:11.707
I don't want to go to 54th and Madison!

22:11.790 --> 22:13.167
Okay, that narrows it down.

22:13.333 --> 22:15.173
I don't want a Sapphire martini
up with olives.

22:15.252 --> 22:17.462
Okay, that narrows it down.

22:17.504 --> 22:19.131
Yeah, you're making kind of a fool
out of yourself.

22:19.214 --> 22:21.258
You can't talk to me
when somebody's standing there.

22:21.300 --> 22:23.969
- Campari and soda.
- Campari soda.

22:24.970 --> 22:26.054
No.

22:27.556 --> 22:30.475
- Pimm's Cup.
- Pimm's Cup.

22:30.517 --> 22:33.228
Pimm's Cup? Pimm's?

22:33.312 --> 22:34.813
- Just get a real drink.
- Shut the fuck up!

22:34.897 --> 22:36.565
Okay! Sorry.

22:36.648 --> 22:40.569
Can I have the first thing I said?

22:40.652 --> 22:42.988
Sapphire martini up with olives.

22:46.992 --> 22:49.620
- Shut up.
- Wow. You need to adjust, right?

22:49.661 --> 22:51.121
No, it's okay, it's okay.

22:51.163 --> 22:53.665
It's okay.
You need a little time to adjust. I get it.

22:53.707 --> 22:55.167
I haven't done jack in 14 months.

22:55.209 --> 22:58.795
- I've been here, believe me, I can wait...
- I died today!

23:01.298 --> 23:02.966
What do you mean?

23:03.634 --> 23:06.261
- I was dead. For seven minutes.
- Yeah?

23:07.095 --> 23:09.014
And then when they brought me back,
I can...

23:09.056 --> 23:11.934
Yeah, well, look, that's the thing.
New York is lousy with ghosts.

23:12.017 --> 23:13.769
I mean, they're everywhere,

23:13.852 --> 23:16.480
and they're a noisy,
pushy, demanding bunch,

23:16.522 --> 23:19.191
same as when they were alive,
and frustrated, too.

23:19.274 --> 23:20.692
The dead have
a lot of unfinished business,

23:20.734 --> 23:22.611
which is why we're still here.

23:22.694 --> 23:24.863
And normally, we can't talk to the living

23:24.947 --> 23:27.324
and, suddenly, you come along,
and you can imagine.

23:27.366 --> 23:29.284
A lot of excitement.

