from his other family.

30:26.952 --> 30:28.620
- I've never seen her before.
- One of those things?

30:28.662 --> 30:31.290
- You stole her cab, remember?
- I've never noticed her, then.

30:31.373 --> 30:33.792
Never noticed her?
Open your eyes, man.

30:33.834 --> 30:35.878
What are you, a brain in a jar?

30:35.961 --> 30:37.921
Okay.
I want to hear what she's got to say.

30:37.963 --> 30:39.131
