in her mind.

31:01.904 --> 31:04.948
- Give her another option.
- I don't get it.

31:05.032 --> 31:07.701
- Present her with an alternative.
- Yeah, yeah, I thought of that.

31:07.784 --> 31:09.495
You mean hire
a good-looking male model...

31:09.578 --> 31:12.247
Don't hire anyone. Don't...
No, don't need...

31:12.331 --> 31:14.666
- Don't need a male model or a fireman.
- Somebody handsome, right?

31:14.750 --> 31:17.544
Not too handsome. Not chiseled,
just approachable. Sort of...

31:17.628 --> 31:19.963
'Cause I was thinking, like,
rugged and somebody tough.

31:20.005 --> 31:23.091
Round-faced, if anything and sensitive.

31:23.175 --> 31:24.801
Well, he's gonna have to have
a lot of cash, though.

31:24.885 --> 31:26.386
If he's sensible with his money,

31:26.470 --> 31:28.305
he's probably invested well,
and that would be attractive.

31:28.347 --> 31:30.015
- Really?
- Yeah.

31:30.098 --> 31:31.725
- She might like that.
- Yeah.

31:31.808 --> 31:33.560
But he's gonna have to be tall.
Tall is important.

31:33.644 --> 31:35.729
No, no, no, no, no, he's not.
No, no. Average.

31:35.812 --> 31:38.524
- Really?
- Yeah. Bordering on the short.

31:39.358 --> 31:41.360
Oh, my word, you mean you.

31:46.657 --> 31:47.991
- I'm... Hey! Hey! Hey!
- Forget it.

31:48.033 --> 31:52.246
Don't walk away mad!
Come here! Pink-Ass!

31:52.371 --> 31:59.294
I would like to elaborate further on
Mummy 1999.1.4's burial site. Here...

31:59.545 --> 32:01.088
- I'm sorry.
- Forget it.

32:01.171 --> 32:05.050
That's okay. I mean, a lot of great ideas
sound completely ridiculous at first.

32:05.133 --> 32:06.343
Sorry I even brought it up.

32:06.385 --> 32:09.555
I'm still thinking about it.
You know, it might work.

32:09.638 --> 32:11.431
I mean, all you're gonna have to do
is be charming enough

32:11.515 --> 32:15.060
to give her a few second thoughts,
you know?

32:15.185 --> 32:16.728
Be a challenge.

32:18.355 --> 32:20.566
Almost impossible.

32:20.649 --> 32:23.110
But I'd be there, you know?
Pulling the strings.

32:23.193 --> 32:27.781
Guy in the bushes calling the plays.
You know, I think I can do it.

32:28.949 --> 32:34.079
- Really. I can do this. I can do it.
- Forget it.

32:34.163 --> 32:35.956
No, no, no, you're not...
You're not married, are you?

32:36.039 --> 32:38.959
- Good God, no.
- No? You got a girlfriend?

32:39.042 --> 32:43.589
No, just between us, currently.

32:44.673 --> 32:49.595
- So you use hookers.
