as you may remember was the case
with Tutankhamen

32:59.271 --> 33:02.107
as shown here on slide 43.

33:02.149 --> 33:03.400
Nope, nope, you know what?

33:03.442 --> 33:05.027
It's possible
that she could actually go for you.

33:05.110 --> 33:09.573
I mean, she likes athletic guys.
I mean, you work out or...

33:09.656 --> 33:10.949
- Yeah?
