33:11.033 --> 33:14.161
- Twice a week. Free weights.
- Okay. All right.

33:14.286 --> 33:16.872
- You got a nice, thick head of hair.
- Protein shampoo.

33:16.955 --> 33:18.248
- She's gonna like that.
- Yeah.

33:18.290 --> 33:20.042
- Look after your scalp.
