the wrappings from the mummy.

33:37.226 --> 33:38.268
I tell you what I'm gonna do.

33:38.310 --> 33:39.811
I'm gonna go over there
when she's finished,

33:39.853 --> 33:42.523
and strike up a conversation with her.

33:43.690 --> 33:45.442
- Yeah.
- I know.

33:47.069 --> 33:49.488
- What?
- I don't know.

33:49.571 --> 33:52.199
I'm just thinking,
in the smock, better not.

33:52.282 --> 33:53.617
- Yes. I came straight from work.
- Okay.

33:53.659 --> 33:56.662
- I'm a dentist. This is what we wear.
- Yeah. Yeah.

33:56.745 --> 34:00.249
- This is how we do it, baby.
- Okay.

34:01.250 --> 34:05.003
And remember that the show officially
opens on Friday, the 12th.

34:05.087 --> 34:07.881
Thank you,
thank you very much for coming.

34:14.513 --> 34:17.683
You know, it's an interesting story.
My daughter went to Egypt.

34:17.766 --> 34:20.060
- Oh, really? Did she?
- Oh, yeah.

34:22.353 --> 34:23.981
Good, all right.

34:27.359 --> 34:29.360
I owe you an apology.

34:31.697 --> 34:35.659
