she didn't come back at all.

58:40.604 --> 58:42.606
Married a man in Portland.

58:45.275 --> 58:46.610
Sorry.

58:51.865 --> 58:54.660
Travel will do that to a relationship.

58:56.537 --> 58:57.913
Yep.

58:57.996 --> 59:01.375
