59:09.508 --> 59:11.260
Because of Richard.

59:12.427 --> 59:13.637
Yeah.

59:15.514 --> 59:17.516
- Good night.
- Good night.

59:22.020 --> 59:25.816
Your story, it's not boring
and ordinary, by the way.

59:26.608 --> 59:29.319
I mean, we just get the one life,
you know?

59:29.361 --> 59:33.824
Just one. You can't live someone else's
or think it's more important,

59:33.866 --> 59:35.909
just because it's more dramatic.

59:35.993 --> 59:37.828
